  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 3. Full 13-factor assessment: 12 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 1 factor (Use error) carried as not-assessed on the basis that analyst judgment considers it inapplicable to a purely computational workflow — however the encoding correctly reflects not-assessed rather than not-applicable.",
